  "auditPreventionRules": [
    {
      "id": "audit-execSync-trycatch-1775047153125",
      "title": "execSync / fs 操作必須包 try-catch",
      "category": "execSync_missing_trycatch",
      "severity": "P0",
      "source": "Pure AI Audit",
      "rule": "### ❌ 禁止：execSync / fs 操作無 try-catch\n所有 execSync / execFileSync / fs.readFileSync / fs.writeFileSync 等危險操作**必須**用 try-catch 包圍。\n\n```javascript\n// ❌ 錯誤 - 無 try-catch，失敗會 crash\nconst result = execSync(command);\n\n// ❌ 錯誤 - async function 入面用 sync 操作\nasync function main() {\n  fs.writeFileSync(file, data); // blocking!\n}\n\n// ✅ 正確 - try-catch 包圍\ntry {\n  const result = execSync(command);\n} catch (e) {\n  console.error(`Command failed: ${e.message}`);\n  return;\n}\n\n// ✅ 正確 - 使用 promises (async)\nasync function main() {\n  await fs.promises.writeFile(file, data);\n}\n```\n\n> 🛡️ **Prevention Rule** (Auto-generated from Pure AI Audit)\n> - 類別: execSync_missing_trycatch\n> - 發現: 3 處問題，受影響: issue_manager.js, session_cleanup.js\n> - 狀態: 已在 AGENTS.md Coding Standards P0 中備案",
      "affectedFiles": [
        "issue_manager.js",
        "session_cleanup.js"
      ],
      "issueCount": 3,
      "applied": true
    },
    {
      "id": "audit-magic-numbers-1775047153125",
      "title": "Magic numbers 必須提升為 CONFIG 常量",
      "category": "magic_numbers",
      "severity": "P1",
      "source": "Pure AI Audit",
      "rule": "### ❌ 禁止：Hardcoded magic numbers\n所有 hardcoded 數字應提升為命名常量，放在 CONFIG 物件頂部。\n\n```javascript\n// ❌ 錯誤 - magic numbers 不可讀\nif (diff > 180 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000) // 180 days expressed as ms\n\n// ✅ 正確 - CONFIG 常量\nconst CONFIG = {\n  THIRTY_DAYS_MS: 180 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000, // 180 days in ms\n  CHANNEL_ID: process.env.DISCORD_CHANNEL_ID,\n  OFFLINE_THRESHOLD_MIN: 3,\n  SSH_TIMEOUT_SEC: 5,\n};\nif (diff > CONFIG.THIRTY_DAYS_MS)\n\n// ✅ 正確 - 多個相關值用 object group\nconst SCAN_CONFIG = {\n  maxFileSize: 100 * 1024,     // 100KB\n  progressInterval: 10,        // 每 N 個檔案輸出一次\n  maxDepth: 20,\n  maxRetries: 5,\n  retryDelay_MS: 100,\n};\n```\n\n> 🛡️ **Prevention Rule** (Auto-generated from Pure AI Audit)\n> - 類別: magic_numbers\n> - 發現: 10 處問題，受影響: pure_ai_audit.js, heartbeat.sh, error_logger.js, error_tracker.js, memory_temporal_search.js, session_cleanup.js, memory_section_cleanup.js, idex_fetcher.js\n> - 狀態: 已在 AGENTS.md Coding Standards P1 中備案",
      "affectedFiles": [
